{"lemma":"بارّ","slug":"بارّ","root":"ب.ر.#","root_slug":"ب-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1658","n2159","n3520"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to perish","examples":[{"text":"ولكن التجارة الناجحة الرابحة التي تدر على صاحبها أضعافا مضاعفة على وجه الاستمرار بلا بوار تلك التجارة هي في الإكثار من الكلم الطيب والعمل الصالح","english":"But successful and profitable trade which increases its owner multiple fold on the face of continuation without ruin, this trade is through increasing in good words and righteous deeds"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lie fallow, be uncultivated (land)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be futile, unsuccessful, unprofitable, lead to nothing (work)","examples":[{"text":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَتْلُونَ كِتَـٰبَ ٱللَّهِ وَأَقَامُوا۟ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ وَأَنفَقُوا۟ مِمَّا رَزَقْنَـٰهُمْ سِرًّۭا وَعَلَانِيَةًۭ يَرْجُونَ تِجَـٰرَةًۭ لَّن تَبُورَ ٢٩","english":"Indeed, those who recite the Book of Allāh and establish prayer and spend [in His cause] out of what We have provided them, secretly and publicly, [can] expect a transaction [i.e., profit] that will never perish -"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be unsalable, be dead stock (merchandise)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bar (place where alcoholic beverages are sold)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of بَرَّ (barra)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From English bar.\n\nDerived from the active participle of the verb بَرَّ (barra)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1658","headword_ar":"بَاَرَ","root":"bA^r","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sunk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dug,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,) a well; (S, M;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtA^r","text_ar":"ابتار","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b2-  Also, aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baA^orN","text_ar":"بَاْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He dug a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollow such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buw^orap","text_ar":"بُوْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which to cook."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S.) ―         -b3-  Also, (T, S, M, K,) aor. as above, (M, K,) and so the inf. n.; (M;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtA^r","text_ar":"ابتار","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing: (T, M, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stored"},{"kind":"text","text":"it, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"laid"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"up, for a time of need."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K.) Hence a hollow dug in the ground is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buw^orapN","text_ar":"بُوْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) ―         -b4-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayorFA","text_ar":"خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtA^r","text_ar":"ابتار","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baA^arahu","text_ar":"بَاَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did good beforehand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K:) or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he, as it were, did good beforehand for himself, having laid it up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed it, for himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) so says El-Umawee: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he laid up for himself in store concealed good:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did good concealedly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ay^tbr","text_ar":"ايتبر"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","AZ","T","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n2159","headword_ar":"بَارٌّ","root":"br","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bar~N","text_ar":"بَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3520","headword_ar":"بَارَ","root":"bwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabuwru","text_ar":"يَبُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaArN","text_ar":"بَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buwrN","text_ar":"بُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, S, M, Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAduwA wa baAruwA","text_ar":"بَادُوا وَ بَارُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They became extinct, and perished"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baArati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"بَارَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The land was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt, state, and uncultivated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was unsown."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAra Eamaluhu","text_ar":"بَارَ عَمَلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His work was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proved, vain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ineffectual:"},{"kind":"text","text":"such is the signification of the verb in the Kur xxxv. 11. (S, K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAra","text_ar":"بَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, &c.,) aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaArN","text_ar":"بَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, Msb, or commodity, T, S, A, Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, unsaleable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult of sale,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in little demand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, A, Mgh, Msb:) because a thing, when neglected, becomes of no use, and thus resembles that which perishes. (Msb.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baArati Als~uwqu","text_ar":"بَارَتِ السُّوقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaArN","text_ar":"بَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The market was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, stagnant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dull, with respect to traffic."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baArati AlA^ay~imu","text_ar":"بَارَتِ الاَيِّمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaArN","text_ar":"بَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The woman without a husband was not desired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought for:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remained in her house long without being demanded in marriage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.) ―         -b7-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAra","text_ar":"بَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as an imitative sequent of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAra","text_ar":"حَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAy^irN","text_ar":"بَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^irN","text_ar":"حَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see exs. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwr","text_ar":"حور"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAra Aln~aAqapa","text_ar":"بَارَ النَّاقَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, A, K,) aor. as above, (T, S, A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought the she-camel to the stallion to see if she were pregnant or not:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, A, K:) for if she is pregnant, she voids her urine in his face (S, K) when he smells her. (S.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the stallion)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smelt the she-camel to know if she were pregnant or not;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtArhA","text_ar":"ابتارها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, M.) ―         -b3-  Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buro liY maA Eanoda fulaAnK","text_ar":"بُرْ لِى مَا عَنْدَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Try thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"examine, and learn, for me, what is in the mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafos","text_ar":"نَفْس"},{"kind":"text","text":"S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A. *) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baArahu","text_ar":"بَارَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, K,) aor. as above, (T, S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, M, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtArhu","text_ar":"ابتارهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AibotiyaArN","text_ar":"اِبْتِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He tried him; assayed him; proved him by experiment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experience; examined him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K.) ElKumeyt says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      pi A_im~aA A@botihaArFA w A_im~aA A@botiyaAraA \n                      \n                     \n                        qabiyHN bimivoliYa naEotu AlfataA"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It were foul in the like of me to characterize the damsel either by false accusation or by trying, with speaking truth, to elicit what is in her mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EinodahaA","text_ar":"مَا عِنْدَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiY nafosihaA","text_ar":"مَا فِى نَفْسِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with an explanation given above]): (S, TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtyArA","text_ar":"ابتيارا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", here signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by asserting with truth my having had sexual intercourse with her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtArhA","text_ar":"ابتارها"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he asserted with truth that he had had sexual intercourse with her;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbthrhA","text_ar":"ابتهرها"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ he asserted the same falsely: ” (A 'Obeyd, T:) and the former signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had sexual intercourse with her"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by force; he ravished her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtAr","text_ar":"ابتار"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he charged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upbraided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a person"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with that which was not in him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abthr","text_ar":"ابتهر"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ he charged, or upbraided, with that which was in him. ” (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bhr","text_ar":"بهر"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","Lth","T","K","A","Mgh","TA"]}]}}